parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Reporting of Safety Recalls and EWR
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of transparency and inconsistent reporting of safety recalls and Early Warning Reports (EWR) can lead to a lack of awareness among consumers about potential safety issues, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Consumers are not informed about safety recalls or EWR
identical vehicles sold in other countries have recalls for the same issues
but not in the USA
manufacturers are not held accountable for reporting safety issues.
